title: Small Upper Level Studio   @ 3023 Lyndale
posting_body: ['* Nice Small Upper level Studio unit has lots of light,  Open kitchen, and carpet just a couple of blocks to the city lakes', "You can't beat the location of the wonderful brick building at 3023 Lyndale Ave.", 'South Avenue', '*', "Within walking distance of the lakes anid all of Uptown's amazing restaurants, Up-Down , coffee shops, nightlife, boutiques, national stores, salons, grocery stores, and movie theatres.", 'Walk, bike, kayak at the Lakes just a couple of blocks away.', '* Work out at CorePower Yoga, Lifetime Fitness, and the YWCA.', '* Minutes to downtown with easy access to bike on the Greenway or take the bus', '* We pay heat, water, electricity ,trash.', '* On-site laundry', '*Email or call Jim', 'show contact info', 'to set up your appointment today!', 'Washer and dryer in the building .', 'Parking is available @ $40.00 monthly.', 'ONE YEAR LEASE ------NO PETS-------THIS IS A NON SMOKING BUILDING-------------------', 'Good credit + clean background check, minimum verifiable monthly income must be at least 3 times monthly rent amount, good rental history, No UDs, No Evictions, Not a Section 8 certified building.', 'Application fee is a non refundable $40.00 (includes the background check)', 'Deposit is 1-months rent ($690.00) -- -- -- -- --', 'We no longer accept applications from smokers !', 'We do not work with subsidy or vouchers programs.']
